sorry, I had mentioned only issue related to autogen.sh

There was this other one,

protobuf, googletest are getting downloaded under downloads folder,
when build command is issued, protoc missing error as it expects googletest and googlemock to be present in specific order under protobuf, {debug info was not enough to catch this at first sight}.

just to make sure nobody gets stuck, please check information provided on readme is enough to get hexagon graph up and running.

thanks.

body:
sorry, I had mentioned only issue related to autogen.sh

There was this other one,

protobuf, googletest are getting downloaded under downloads folder,
 when build command is issued, `protoc missing error` as it expects googletest and googlemock to be present in specific order under protobuf, {debug info was not enough to catch this at first sight}.

just to make sure nobody gets stuck, please check information provided on readme is enough to get hexagon graph up and running.

thanks.
